                                        </th>
                                        <th
                                            class="border-r border-blue-400 p-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                            Rol (String)
                                        </th>
                                        <th
                                            class="border-r border-orange-400 p-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800">
