                </div>

                <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    <p>Hi team,</p>
                    <p>Following up on our discussion yesterday regarding the new contract clauses.</p>
                    <p>I've attached the finalized financial report for Q3 along with the updated MSA draft. Our legal
                        team has already reviewed the redlines from your side.</p>
                    <p>Please review it and provide your final approval by EOD Friday, October 28th, 2024, so we can
                        proceed with the signing next week.</p>
                    <p>Best regards,<br>John</p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex space-x-3">
                    <div
                        class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center bg-gray-50 w-64 hover:bg-gray-100 cursor-pointer transition-colors">
