            <div class="px-6 py-2 bg-indigo-900 text-white flex justify-between items-center text-sm font-medium">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-indigo-300 mr-2"></i> Sugerencias Inteligentes de IA
                    (Copiloto)
                </div>
