                        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-3 border-b border-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-800 uppercase tracking-wider"><i
                                    class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text mr-1"></i> Borrador M365 (Respuesta
                                Bilingüe)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 flex-1">
                            <div
                                class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-600 italic mb-3">
                                "Hello John, Thank you for the update. We have received the financial report for Q3 and
                                the MSA draft. Our team will review it and get back to you by the deadline this
                                Friday..."
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-auto" x-show="!done">
                                <button class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-red-500 font-medium">Descargar</button>
                                <button @click="done = true"
                                    class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-sm">
                                    <i class="fa-regular fa-paper-plane mr-1"></i> Insertar y Abrir Modal
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div x-show="done"
                                class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm text-green-600 bg-green-50 p-2 rounded">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mr-2"></i> Borrador inyectado en O365
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

</body>

</html>
